%HRTitleEvent Cue-bid
%bridge-classroom-stable: true
%bridge-context: Support cue-bid = limit raise+ with trump support
{You have a limit raise in \Hs; if East had not overcalled you would have bid 3\H. 

Instead, you cue-bid 2\S, promising at least 11 points and support for \Hs. Partner bids 3\H.  

Pass. Partner indicates a minimum hand and you don't have enough extra to bid more.}

